          "name": "Call the Attack",
          "description": "STRATEGIC GAMBIT if this operative doesn't have one of your Frenzy tokens. Select one friendly FELLGOR RAVAGER operative visible to and within 6\" of this operative. That selected operative, and each other friendly FELLGOR RAVAGER operative visible to and within 2\" of it, can immediately perform a free Dash action in an order of your choice."
        }
      ],
